You need to install php-dbus using the instructions in
misc/HOWTO.BuildPhpDbus

You need to open DBus security up using the instructions in
misc/HOWTO.ConfigureDbusSecurity

You need to build the misc/discid binary using the instruction in 
misc/HOWTO.BuildDiscId

You need to install Doctrine ORM 2.x and configure a database using
the instructions in
misc/HOWTO.InstallDoctrineORM

Here are some commands you can run: 

To clear out memcache.
$ bin/clear_memcached

To execute doctrine CLI commands (see misc/HOWTO.InstallDoctrineORM).
$ bin/doctrine

To monitor all the optical drives for disc insertion and start ripping
automatically.
$ bin/monitor_media
